name: (Unofficial)DallasCowboysFlashBriefing
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
This is a flash briefing skill designed by ButtonPushApps to provide listeners with the latest news on the NFL Dallas Cowboys. I used the RSS feed fromKENS5 Sports: http://rssfeeds.kens5.com/kens5/highschoolsports

I plan to add more feeds from reputable sports reporting services in the near future.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
